msgid ""
"Your map is a means to communicate information (as well as new ideas and "
"you) to the map reader.  You use symbology to convey the contents of your "
"data so it can be easily understood. When you create a map layout, you go "
"one step further - you present your map so that it becomes a means of "
"information."
